    "4009021": {
        "Desc": "Complete the second round of the Test of Courage",
        "Step": "You decided to join Sayu in the second round. What challenges will you encounter along the way?",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Uhh, hellooo? Miss shrine maiden...? Strange, she isn't here."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Waaaah! What's this? Look, there's something written in red on the bulletin board!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "\"Round 3... Item... Hagoita.\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Does this mean that the item we have to find in the third round is a hagoita?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Shikanoin Heizou",
                    "T": "The shrine maiden appears to be urging us to finish the third round of the Test of Courage."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "But where did she go?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "*gasp* Has she been taken away by a ghost!?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Will Paimon be next!? *gulp* Oh, Paimon won't ever leave your side now!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Shikanoin Heizou",
                    "T": "The words are scribbled hastily, but there's no evidence of a struggle. However... aren't there too many words written here?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "What did you notice, Heizou?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Shikanoin Heizou",
                    "T": "I believe that the three items chosen for this three-round contest were each selected by the three organizing parties."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Shikanoin Heizou",
                    "T": "The Dango Milk was chosen by the merchant who funded the event, and the fan was chosen by the Yashiro Commission, which provided the staff."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Shikanoin Heizou",
                    "T": "So, does the hagoita, which should have been chosen by the Grand Narukami Shrine, have any unique significance?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Let's worry about that later. The bigger question is, are we really going to join the third round of the Test of Courage?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Paimon would love to win the grand prize, but our safety comes first!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "How about we... make a tactical retreat!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Shikanoin Heizou",
                    "T": "I still have my commission to complete, so I'll stay."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Shikanoin Heizou",
                    "T": "Fear arises from mystery, and it's a detective's job to unearth the truth from the mystery."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Huh, Paimon somehow feels a little better after hearing you say that..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Okay then, let's wait for a while."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Maybe the shrine maiden had something to take care of and will be back soon..."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
